headline: Duke Energy prepares for potential severe storms in Indiana, urges customers to be ready
summary: Duke Energy is monitoring forecasts and preparing for potential severe weather, including strong thunderstorms and damaging winds, that may bring widespread outages to its Indiana service territory this weekend.
